  "texts": [
    "However, a trend was apparent for a larger decrease in the hybrid-intervention group (control group: T1-T0 = 1.21, T2-T1 = 1.00; tele group: T1-T0 = 1.85, T2-T1 = 0.54).",
    "Similarly, Figure 4 shows a significant decrease over time in the GAD-7 scores (p < 0.001).",
    "The intervention did not have a significant effect on the HQ (p > 0.05).",
